{"tid":2256240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【陳同佳赴台】潘母昨與警聯絡 涉洗黑錢案中女兒證物","createTime":"2020-10-24T07:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T10:56:57.000Z","uid":73092,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"77f0845a438a34328c6591577317ff9a20933339","tid":2256240,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:54:51.000Z","msg":"台灣殺人案疑犯陳同佳在本港出獄一年，至今未獲入台證赴到台自首。死者潘曉穎母親表示，昨晚與警方有聯絡，但只是聯絡她提及交還涉及洗黑錢案中女兒的證物。<br />\n潘母表示，昨天晚上9時接獲電話，但內容並非關於她近日所提希望當中間人，邀請本港警方與台灣警方坐下商討的事，她仍希望本港警方就此事盡快跟她聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共拆唔撚掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925d6d7104023d5a3be39386c5f44b92d75c3fcb","tid":2256240,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0-%E6%BD%98%E6%AF%8D%E6%98%A8%E8%88%87%E8%AD%A6%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1-%E6%B6%89%E6%B4%97%E9%BB%91%E9%8C%A2%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E8%AD%89%E7%89%A9-035300381.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E6%25BD%2598%25E6%25AF%258D%25E6%2598%25A8%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B5%25A1-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%25B4%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E9%258C%25A2%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%2589%25A9-035300381.html&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLD632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=22b3f71b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0-%E6%BD%98%E6%AF%8D%E6%98%A8%E8%88%87%E8%AD%A6%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1-%E6%B6%89%E6%B4%97%E9%BB%91%E9%8C%A2%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E8%AD%89%E7%89%A9-035300381.html</a>"},{"pid":"be0af02b31b4ed4be4ea6525e0ff203e4c63cd14","tid":2256240,"